WEBVTT

00:00:33.437 --> 00:00:37.518
MY NAME IS CAROLINE ISAKOW. TODAY'S DATE IS SUNDAY,

00:00:37.518 --> 00:00:41.346
THE TWENTY SIXTH OF JANUARY, NINETEEN NINETY SEVEN.

00:00:41.503 --> 00:00:45.615
I'M CONDUCTING AN INTERVIEW WITH MR SZLAMA BIRMAN.

00:00:45.738 --> 00:00:50.047
THE INTERVIEW IS BEING CONDUCTED IN THE SUBURB OF ELSTERNWICK,

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:51.751
MELBOURNE AUSTRALIA,

00:00:51.751 --> 00:00:53.057
IN YIDDISH.

00:00:55.188 --> 00:00:56.111
UNK.

00:00:57.348 --> 00:00:58.709
her Birman,

00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:02.271
kenst mir zogn dayn nomen?

00:01:03.086 --> 00:01:04.093
dem nomen.

00:01:04.588 --> 00:01:07.906
se oyf yidish, yo? Shloyme Birman.

00:01:08.756 --> 00:01:10.725
host andere nemen?

00:01:12.165 --> 00:01:16.614
kenst mi- mir zogn ven ir bist geboyrn?

00:01:16.350 --> 00:01:17.087
yo.

00:01:17.649 --> 00:01:19.331
dem tsvelftn MARCH,

00:01:20.028 --> 00:01:22.051
NINETEEN TWELVE.

00:01:22.051 --> 00:01:24.680
ikh ken araynvarfn englishe verter?

00:01:25.952 --> 00:01:28.528
vi alt bist ir haynt?

00:01:28.685 --> 00:01:29.830
EIGHTY FOUR.

00:01:29.830 --> 00:01:32.377
akh- fir un akhtsik yor.

00:01:33.157 --> 00:01:35.986
zog mir, vu bist ir geboyrn?

00:01:36.009 --> 00:01:37.674
geboyrn bin ikh in

00:01:38.034 --> 00:01:39.547
di shtot Varshe

00:01:40.363 --> 00:01:42.416
in Po- in Poyln, in Poyln.

00:01:44.261 --> 00:01:48.373
kenst mir zogn vi dayn foter hot geheysn?

00:01:48.243 --> 00:01:49.233
Mordekhay.

00:01:50.235 --> 00:01:52.373
vi hot dayn muter geheysn?

00:01:52.344 --> 00:01:53.216
Beyle.

00:01:54.892 --> 00:01:58.346
host gehat briders un shvesters in der heym?

00:01:58.335 --> 00:02:01.485
a sh- in der heym nisht, iz zi shoyn geven farheyrat.

00:02:02.368 --> 00:02:05.299
zi iz frier farheyrat vayl zi iz geven di eltste shvester.

00:02:05.557 --> 00:02:08.116
azoy az zi hot zikh gevoynt far zikh mitn man.

00:02:08.308 --> 00:02:11.593
un azoy un di andere zenen mir geven akht brider.

00:02:12.223 --> 00:02:14.563
un ikh bin eyne fun di mitlste.

00:02:15.024 --> 00:02:18.562
kenst mir zogn ale di nemer un

00:02:18.888 --> 00:02:21.144
vi zey kumen ersht,

00:02:21.386 --> 00:02:23.355
ershtn, tsveytn, dritn?

00:02:23.360 --> 00:02:25.382
oyfn onfang fun di yunge?

00:02:25.385 --> 00:02:27.455
fun di eltste onfangen?

00:02:27.596 --> 00:02:29.700
yo, di eltste iz geven di shvester,

00:02:29.992 --> 00:02:31.674
vi azoy zi hot geheysn?

00:02:31.865 --> 00:02:33.077
hot zi geheysn

00:02:33.077 --> 00:02:34.475
Sore Yite.

00:02:35.510 --> 00:02:37.884
un nokh dem iz geven,

00:02:38.042 --> 00:02:40.449
der tsveyter iz geven Binyomin.

00:02:40.893 --> 00:02:44.009
ikh ken nisht alts zogn in yidishn yo? Binyo- nisht BINYAMIN.

00:02:44.859 --> 00:02:45.860
Binyomin,

00:02:45.860 --> 00:02:52.278
nokh dem iz geven Moyshe, nokh dem iz geven Doved,

00:02:53.043 --> 00:02:56.429
nokh dem iz geven Mendl,

00:02:57.532 --> 00:02:59.129
nokh dem bin ikh geven,

00:03:00.738 --> 00:03:02.251
un nokh dem iz gegangen,

00:03:04.316 --> 00:03:05.829
ikh denk gornisht der tsveyter,

00:03:06.240 --> 00:03:07.688
iz geven Yankl,

00:03:07.688 --> 00:03:10.655
un nokh dem iz geven

00:03:11.808 --> 00:03:12.815
Yitskhok,

00:03:13.985 --> 00:03:17.169
un der kleyner, der yingster iz geven Yerakhmil.

00:03:20.111 --> 00:03:23.062
gedenkst di gas un di

00:03:23.062 --> 00:03:26.130
shtub vu du host gevoynt in Varshe?

00:03:25.106 --> 00:03:26.737
yo, yo, yo, yo.

00:03:26.793 --> 00:03:28.115
di gas hot geheysn

00:03:28.143 --> 00:03:29.892
Frantshishkaner-Gas.

00:03:30.219 --> 00:03:31.277
der numer?

00:03:31.248 --> 00:03:32.879
akht un tsvontsik.

00:03:34.944 --> 00:03:36.966
kenst mir zogn

00:03:36.969 --> 00:03:39.883
vos far a shprakh du host geredt in der heym?

00:03:39.990 --> 00:03:41.132
yidish.

00:03:41.188 --> 00:03:44.338
un vos far a shprakh du host geredt in der gas?

00:03:44.360 --> 00:03:46.177
iz geven poylish un,

00:03:46.487 --> 00:03:51.310
se iz geven mit vemen, yunge khevre hobn geredt in poylish,

00:03:51.330 --> 00:03:54.238
vayl zey zenen gegangen in di shuln, zey zenen gegangen in di gimnazyums.

00:03:54.283 --> 00:03:56.862
un in shtub hob ikh zikh oyfgeredt, un se geven a sakh

00:03:56.862 --> 00:03:59.441
mentshn vos ikh hob geredt in yidish in gas oykh.

00:03:59.902 --> 00:04:05.415
azoy az be- mit mit ve- mentshn velkhe me hot zikh getrofn

00:04:05.471 --> 00:04:07.493
vos zey hobn geredt poylish, yidn,

00:04:07.530 --> 00:04:09.465
hob ikh geredt poylish.

00:04:10.719 --> 00:04:13.492
kenst mir zogn

00:04:13.492 --> 00:04:15.759
vi der lebn iz geven

00:04:15.865 --> 00:04:17.631
bay aykh in der heym?

00:04:18.667 --> 00:04:21.665
vos vos heyst azoy, materyelish, oder...

00:04:22.008 --> 00:04:26.593
m- materye- kultur, yidishkeyt.

00:04:23.257 --> 00:04:24.365
in algemeyn.

00:04:25.316 --> 00:04:26.714
kultur azoy der,

00:04:26.714 --> 00:04:28.443
der foter iz geven

00:04:28.443 --> 00:04:30.559
a frumer mentsh, a frumer yid.

00:04:30.969 --> 00:04:34.372
er iz geven er hot gehert tsum Radzominer rebn a mol.

00:04:34.952 --> 00:04:40.110
un di mame farshteyt zikh, az der foter iz geven frum, zi iz gegangen a sheytl ongetun,

00:04:40.233 --> 00:04:43.366
un me hot gefirt a koshere yidishe kokh,

00:04:43.963 --> 00:04:48.665
un dos iz geven dos lebn in der heym. shabes iz men gegangen davenen tsuzamen

00:04:48.738 --> 00:04:50.622
mitn foter in shul arayn,

00:04:50.780 --> 00:04:54.116
un me iz geven in di ershte yorn me iz geven yung,

00:04:54.189 --> 00:04:55.263
hot men zikh

00:04:55.488 --> 00:04:58.452
gehaltn mitn tatn, di religye mitgehaltn,

00:04:58.543 --> 00:05:01.291
di yom toyvim iz geven traditsyonel,

00:05:01.310 --> 00:05:03.937
azoy az dos iz gegangen dos lebn in der heym.

00:05:04.449 --> 00:05:07.177
kenst mir zogn

00:05:08.668 --> 00:05:14.434
a bayshpil, a fraytik bay der nakht o shabes, ver iz gezesn barn tish?

00:05:14.439 --> 00:05:17.437
az di gantse mishpokhe un di mame hot zikh geporet.

00:05:17.696 --> 00:05:20.728
di mame hot badorfn tsugebn, zi hot zikh avekgezetst nakher.

00:05:20.868 --> 00:05:24.271
zi hot badorfn tsugebn, se geven keyn eynhore a tish mit mentshn,

00:05:24.328 --> 00:05:26.837
bridern hob ikh gehat zeyer a sakh, der tate,

00:05:27.095 --> 00:05:29.384
azoy az se geven

00:05:29.660 --> 00:05:30.987
a groyse mishpokhe.

00:05:31.398 --> 00:05:34.987
un di mame hot undz badint, tsugegebn, se geven a shtikl arbet.

00:05:34.993 --> 00:05:39.392
un vos hot zi gekokhn? vos vos gedenkst,

00:05:39.650 --> 00:05:40.741
alts iz geven,

00:05:39.954 --> 00:05:41.771
ah ir geven oyfn tish?

00:05:41.591 --> 00:05:44.910
oyfn tish iz geven a traditsyoneler shabes.

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:49.112
iz geven fish, dos iz dos ershte, on fish iz nisht geven keyn shabes,

00:05:49.252 --> 00:05:51.913
un nokh dem hot men tsugegebn, oder a yoykh

00:05:52.509 --> 00:05:54.528
un nokh dem iz geven fleysh

00:05:54.635 --> 00:05:58.764
un nokh dem iz geven a DESSERT, dos iz a kompot

00:05:58.989 --> 00:06:00.182
in yidishn.

00:06:00.474 --> 00:06:01.903
un THAT'S ALL.

00:06:04.187 --> 00:06:09.125
AND vos iz geven dayn foter's arbet?

00:06:08.979 --> 00:06:11.572
foter arbet hot gehat in shtub

00:06:12.303 --> 00:06:18.389
a WORKSHOP, dos iz ikh zog es shoyn in in a andere shprakh,

00:06:19.070 --> 00:06:23.252
in a WORKSHOP, un azoy hot er gehat tsvey sezonen iz es geven,

00:06:23.255 --> 00:06:25.139
vinter tsayt hot er gehat

00:06:25.196 --> 00:06:27.589
in gantsn a bazundere

00:06:27.589 --> 00:06:29.291
vi der zumer tsayt.

00:06:31.338 --> 00:06:32.125
arbet.

00:06:32.621 --> 00:06:35.990
azoy az vinter hot er, ho'mir gemakht KNITTING,

00:06:36.266 --> 00:06:40.378
hot oysgearbet PULLOVERS CARDIGANS,

00:06:40.518 --> 00:06:43.755
un un ale hobn mitgearbet, ikh hob mitgearbet,

00:06:43.792 --> 00:06:48.219
un un zumer tsayt hot er gearbet oys sandaln,

00:06:48.247 --> 00:06:50.582
far kinder, shikhlekh far kinder,

00:06:50.610 --> 00:06:53.811
hot men gehat di mashinen in shtub, un me hot dos

00:06:54.255 --> 00:06:57.349
un me iz ales gegangen azoy mashinove, se nisht gegangen mit keyn hent,

00:06:57.349 --> 00:06:59.531
se nisht keyn shuster arbet, dos iz geven

00:06:59.604 --> 00:07:00.830
mashin arbet.

00:07:01.697 --> 00:07:04.037
vi groys iz di shtub geven?

00:07:03.418 --> 00:07:05.314
iz geven zeyer a kleyne shtub.

00:07:05.342 --> 00:07:07.884
se iz geven tsvey shtiber un a kokh.

00:07:08.497 --> 00:07:09.976
mitn varshtat,

00:07:10.083 --> 00:07:11.461
mit di kinderlekh,

00:07:11.923 --> 00:07:15.883
un kinderlekh in eyn, shlofn in eyn bet tsvey kinderlekh,

00:07:16.158 --> 00:07:19.021
azoy az se iz geven a bisl shver dos lebn.

00:07:20.411 --> 00:07:23.561
un di muter, zi hot gearbet?

00:07:23.111 --> 00:07:24.407
neyn. UNK

00:07:24.427 --> 00:07:27.560
tsu firn aza virtshaft hot zi nokh gekent arbetn?

00:07:27.701 --> 00:07:30.412
zi hot genug arbet far azoy fil kinder in shtub.

00:07:33.219 --> 00:07:36.034
AND vos hostu,

00:07:36.037 --> 00:07:38.529
vos far a shule bistu gegangen?

00:07:38.298 --> 00:07:41.634
oy ikh, keyn hoykh shule bin ikh nisht gegangen,

00:07:41.690 --> 00:07:45.363
koydem bin ikh di ershte tsayt ven ikh bin nokh geven yung, gegangen in a kheyder,

00:07:45.892 --> 00:07:47.172
mit a melamed.

00:07:47.192 --> 00:07:49.332
dos iz in di yidishe shtibn

00:07:49.352 --> 00:07:51.720
in di khsidishe shtibn dos ershte geven

00:07:51.731 --> 00:07:52.789
a kheyder.

00:07:52.929 --> 00:07:55.573
nakher hob ikh ongehoybn tsu geyn in dem,

00:07:56.186 --> 00:07:58.290
vi nokh heyst es, in Yidishn,

00:07:58.852 --> 00:08:03.035
POVSHEKHNE, Yidishn,

00:08:03.035 --> 00:08:07.126
der nider, nider SCHOOL, der onfang fun a kind in di SCHOOL.

00:08:07.126 --> 00:08:10.406
vi nokh heyst es do? di PR- PRIMARY SCHOOL.

00:08:08.617 --> 00:08:09.483
PRIMARY

00:08:11.222 --> 00:08:13.275
un dos iz alts.

00:08:13.466 --> 00:08:16.093
nokh hob ikh shoyn gemuzt geyn aheym in shtub arayn,

00:08:16.250 --> 00:08:19.417
mithelfn dem tatn arbetn, vayl er hot nisht gekent,

00:08:19.777 --> 00:08:22.708
er iz nisht umshtand tsu nemen mentshn

00:08:22.815 --> 00:08:26.050
un batsoln far mentshn, azoy az me hot mitgearbet mit im.

00:08:27.624 --> 00:08:33.340
un di shule, vos far a shprakh hobn zey geredt in di shule?

00:08:32.433 --> 00:08:35.313
in di shule, se iz geven a yidishe shul,

00:08:35.488 --> 00:08:39.535
nor se iz gekumen a lerer f- vos hobn gelernt poylish,

00:08:39.572 --> 00:08:42.705
di poylishe shprakh. un azoy se iz gegangen yidishe shprakh.

00:08:42.828 --> 00:08:46.099
afilek gelernt gemore,

00:08:46.119 --> 00:08:48.594
se geven a yidishe, a yidishe shul.

00:08:49.427 --> 00:08:53.099
azoy az poylish hot er gelernt a poylisher lerer.

00:08:55.383 --> 00:08:58.972
AND host gehobt fraynt?

00:08:59.028 --> 00:09:02.229
oh yo, a sakh fraynt. in di yunge yorn zeyer a sakh.

00:09:03.298 --> 00:09:05.655
gehat meydlekh, yinglekh tsuzamen.

00:09:07.449 --> 00:09:13.738
AND ale andere kinder zenen oykhet geganen in kheyder, in frume shules?

00:09:12.292 --> 00:09:14.514
yo, ale kinder. ale kinder

00:09:14.891 --> 00:09:16.995
hobn adurkhgemakht di kheyder tsayt.

00:09:18.587 --> 00:09:24.473
un kenst mir zogn dayn foter hot a mol geforn tsu der re- tsu im's rebe?

00:09:23.261 --> 00:09:26.692
oh yo! di ale yontoy- di ale yo-

00:09:24.473 --> 00:09:26.765
fregn shayles, o bazukhn?

00:09:26.692 --> 00:09:28.166
di ale yontoyvim,

00:09:28.425 --> 00:09:30.110
ale yontoyvim iz er geven.

00:09:30.112 --> 00:09:31.991
farshteyt zikh nisht in sukes,

00:09:31.991 --> 00:09:33.408
nisht in peysekh,

00:09:33.453 --> 00:09:35.323
nor rosheshone yomkiper,

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:37.585
dos iz ale yorn geforn

00:09:37.585 --> 00:09:38.589
tsum rebn

00:09:38.589 --> 00:09:41.159
un er hot mitgenumen tsvey dray kinder mit zikh.

00:09:41.537 --> 00:09:44.417
keyn Radzomin, vayl dos iz geven a Radzominer rebe.

00:09:44.709 --> 00:09:47.167
un vi vayt iz dos fun Varshe?

00:09:47.662 --> 00:09:49.766
se iz a bisl vayt, se iz

00:09:49.923 --> 00:09:51.895
keyn groyse shtreke iz dos nisht.

00:09:51.915 --> 00:09:56.223
se iz geven, me iz geforn mit a ban keyn keyn Radzomin, se iz geven nisht vayt fun Varshe.

00:09:56.268 --> 00:09:58.912
ken nisht genoy zogn vifl kilometer se iz geven.

00:10:00.555 --> 00:10:03.418
vi lang iz er ve- geven avek fun der heym?

00:10:03.002 --> 00:10:07.249
di di gantse yontoyvim iz geven dort. me iz nisht ahin geforn, aher geforn.

00:10:07.473 --> 00:10:12.108
geven tsvey tog rosheshone ken men nisht tsurikforn, vayl me tor nisht forn shabes

00:10:12.266 --> 00:10:13.374
un yontev.

00:10:14.966 --> 00:10:18.468
SO di muter, vu iz di muter geven in zelbe tsayt?

00:10:16.974 --> 00:10:19.331
neyn, di muter iz geblibn in shtub, yo.

00:10:20.130 --> 00:10:23.061
nor di mener zenen avekgeforn, di yinglekh mitn tatn.

00:10:24.737 --> 00:10:27.381
un kenst mir zogn

00:10:27.943 --> 00:10:30.502
in vos hostu dikh farnumen

00:10:30.930 --> 00:10:33.692
nisht in arbeter tsayt?

00:10:33.596 --> 00:10:35.345
yo, ikh hob geven

00:10:35.486 --> 00:10:36.901
in a sport klub

00:10:36.903 --> 00:10:38.382
in di yunge yorn.

00:10:38.642 --> 00:10:42.113
se oyb du veyst, se iz gants bakant der nomen Makabi,

00:10:42.607 --> 00:10:44.761
un dortn hob ikh zeyer farbrengt ovntn.

00:10:45.105 --> 00:10:47.793
in sport zeyer a sakh, ober ales so- sort.

00:10:47.838 --> 00:10:49.992
ale sort sportn genutst.

00:10:50.201 --> 00:10:54.050
bin geven farnumen di gantse tsayt mit sport, ikh hob zeyer lib gehat sport.

00:10:53.897 --> 00:10:55.495
gib mit a bayshpil.

00:10:55.348 --> 00:10:58.076
a bayshpil, ikh bin geven, oyf english vel ikh dir zogn,

00:10:58.487 --> 00:11:00.000
a ICE SKATER,

00:11:00.208 --> 00:11:01.598
ersht bin ikh geven

00:11:01.598 --> 00:11:04.505
a BICYCLE, oyf di loyf.

00:11:04.747 --> 00:11:06.682
un nokh dem bin ikh geven

00:11:07.464 --> 00:11:09.669
ikh bin a bisl, di ershte tsayt, geven

00:11:09.860 --> 00:11:12.203
opge- ayngefangen in BOX,

00:11:12.203 --> 00:11:15.558
vayl ikh bin geven gut geboyt, ikh hob, zey hobn mikh tsugenumen.

00:11:14.619 --> 00:11:15.744
BOXING?

00:11:15.817 --> 00:11:19.153
bite? BOXING, bin ikh geven a,

00:11:16.222 --> 00:11:17.381
BOXING?

00:11:19.698 --> 00:11:21.009
nisht azoy lang.

00:11:21.217 --> 00:11:25.247
ikh bin nisht gegangen tsu di hoykhe klase, ober ikh bin geven, in di onfang bin ikh geven

00:11:25.284 --> 00:11:28.336
gut in BOX, un ikh bin geven gimnastik,

00:11:28.336 --> 00:11:30.375
zeyer a sakh gimnastik gemakht,

00:11:30.583 --> 00:11:32.411
un un vos iz nokh dortn geven?

00:11:32.411 --> 00:11:34.138
yo, shvimen, dos ershte,

00:11:34.768 --> 00:11:38.087
shvimen zeyer a sakh, vayl Makabi hot gehat a stadyon

00:11:38.312 --> 00:11:40.146
oyb du veyst Vaysl,

00:11:40.893 --> 00:11:42.659
dos iz a taykh

00:11:42.783 --> 00:11:44.786
vos iz adurkhgelofn Varshe.

00:11:45.180 --> 00:11:47.554
un zey hobn gehat an eygenem stadyon,

00:11:48.420 --> 00:11:51.300
un dort hot men zeyer a sakh farbrengt in zumer tsayt,

00:11:51.710 --> 00:11:53.291
un di sheyne vetern.

00:11:53.668 --> 00:11:55.097
me iz geshvumen a sakh,

00:11:55.338 --> 00:11:57.357
me hot ge- vi nokh heyst es, ge-

00:11:59.507 --> 00:12:01.931
geshprungen fun trampolins, veyst dokh,

00:12:03.152 --> 00:12:05.661
fun azoy hoykhe trampolins bin ikh geshpru-

00:12:06.577 --> 00:12:08.920
un azoy az ikh hob farbrengt in dos,

00:12:08.920 --> 00:12:10.304
farshteyt zikh az me iz gegangen,

00:12:10.304 --> 00:12:13.620
ikh hob dokh nisht gekent ale tog, se geven shabes, se geven z- hot men zikh getrofn

00:12:13.620 --> 00:12:16.798
mit meydlekh, mit yinglekh, me hot zikh gemakht azelkhe

00:12:17.124 --> 00:12:20.409
azelkhe PITCHETCHKES heyst es in poylish.

00:12:22.693 --> 00:12:26.977
zog mir, dayn foter iz geven a khosid, vos

00:12:25.391 --> 00:12:26.473
yo.

00:12:26.977 --> 00:12:32.258
far, vos hot er geklert ven er hot gezen az du

00:12:32.258 --> 00:12:36.541
