00:23:41.538 --> 00:23:44.904
un zey hobn nokh gemakht azelkhe khazeray mit mit shtekens,

00:23:44.904 --> 00:23:46.574
hobn zey nokh arayngeleygt

00:23:46.574 --> 00:23:48.566
in der ek fun shtekn aza

00:23:48.594 --> 00:23:51.013
aza zhilet vos me razirt zikh,

00:23:51.041 --> 00:23:52.740
az se zol zayn sharf azelkhe.

00:23:53.083 --> 00:23:56.995
zeyer a zeyer a shver dos, ikh, ikh hob shoyn nisht gekent aroys

00:23:56.995 --> 00:23:58.494
bin ikh ariber bay dem

00:23:58.820 --> 00:24:00.620
GATE, vi nokh heyst es, iber dem,

00:24:00.778 --> 00:24:03.202
dos hot pasirt UNK.

00:24:01.993 --> 00:24:06.004
oft. dort iz geven oft. vayl dort iz geven zeyer a sheyner park,

00:24:06.127 --> 00:24:08.214
in mitn iz geven a vaser,

00:24:08.388 --> 00:24:09.851
iz geven zeyer sheyn.

00:24:10.363 --> 00:24:14.393
iz dos iz geven, se geven zeyer a sakh faln, ikh ken UNK.

00:24:14.393 --> 00:24:16.958
se geven an ander park, hot es geheysn

00:24:16.958 --> 00:24:18.389
TRAGUTA Park,

00:24:18.632 --> 00:24:21.242
iz in eyn zayt hot es gehert,

00:24:21.348 --> 00:24:22.923
a halbe park kimat

00:24:22.923 --> 00:24:26.771
in gegnt tsu di kristlekhn gegnt, in di zayt hot gehert tsu di yidishe.

00:24:26.799 --> 00:24:28.476
hobn zikh gemakht azelkhe

00:24:28.476 --> 00:24:30.961
bandes, dos heyst azelkhe grupn,

00:24:31.608 --> 00:24:34.302
groyse grupn, un yeder ovnt,

00:24:34.393 --> 00:24:38.893
un mir ho'mir gevust mentshn, yidn zitsn in dem park, vos der zayt fun dem yidishn gegnt,

00:24:39.101 --> 00:24:42.659
hobn zey ge- shtendik, nakht bay nakht iz geven a ⟨kamer⟩, vos iz?

00:24:42.659 --> 00:24:44.549
der yidisher yugnt iz nisht geven

00:24:44.585 --> 00:24:48.360
azoy tsurikgeshlogn, zey hobn gekent tsurikgebn a klap.

00:24:48.703 --> 00:24:53.355
azoy az me iz, undz zenen UNK aroys mit di zelbe zakhn, mit shtekens, mit andere

00:24:53.462 --> 00:24:55.172
un un me hot ongehoybn

00:24:55.217 --> 00:25:00.257
tsu hargenen zey aroys, zenen ongefaln oyf mentshn vos zenen gezitsn oyf benk, yidn,

00:25:00.363 --> 00:25:03.052
un a bisl ge⟨UNK⟩ un ongefaln,

00:25:03.097 --> 00:25:05.568
dos iz geven a tog teglekher ershaynung.

00:25:06.354 --> 00:25:08.435
un me hot gelitn a bisl fun di khevre.

00:25:08.463 --> 00:25:10.887
a mol zikh arayngerisn in yidishn gegnt,

00:25:10.944 --> 00:25:12.941
vayle mayn hot zikh ge-

00:25:12.941 --> 00:25:16.322
gegrenetst mit a kristlekher gas, se hot geheysn FRETA,

00:25:16.614 --> 00:25:20.591
un un dortn hobn zikh a mol arayngerisn oyf undzer gas arayn

00:25:20.816 --> 00:25:23.268
un oyf undzer gas hot nisht gefelt keyn bisl,

00:25:23.313 --> 00:25:26.210
iz geven furmanes, veyst dokh, iz geven a bisl,

00:25:26.537 --> 00:25:29.571
trogn- tregers hot men zey gerufn,

00:25:29.571 --> 00:25:32.187
zey hobn gefirt di droshkes hobn zey gefirt,

00:25:32.187 --> 00:25:34.226
dos zenen ge- dos iz geven lebs-yinglekh.

00:25:34.535 --> 00:25:37.325
hobn zey aroysgenumen fun di droshkes aroys dem,

00:25:37.325 --> 00:25:39.865
dem vi di ferd vert ayngeshpant,

00:25:39.865 --> 00:25:43.198
aroysgenumen fun di droshkes un arayn in dem dort vu di

00:25:43.226 --> 00:25:45.400
vu di shkotsim, heysn dos,

00:25:45.437 --> 00:25:47.861
a sheygets, veyst vos heyst a shey- a kristlekh yingl,

00:25:47.917 --> 00:25:51.286
UNK zenen ongefaln un zey hobn zey dort gemakht a khurve.

00:25:51.444 --> 00:25:56.771
se ongekumen politsey, me hot gornisht keynem gekent khapn. dos iz dort geven ⟨oft sheyn un gor⟩.

00:25:57.097 --> 00:25:59.909
azoy az se iz geven a shver shtikl lebn dort.

00:26:00.658 --> 00:26:04.247
se geven in di yidn, tsvishn di yidn, hot men zikh gelebt gants

00:26:04.556 --> 00:26:06.967
freylekh, say in yom toyvim gefirt,

00:26:06.967 --> 00:26:09.698
se gekumen a yontev iz geven alts farmakht,

00:26:09.804 --> 00:26:12.988
in yidishn gegnt, keyn gesheft hot nisht gekent oyfefenen zikh.

00:26:13.061 --> 00:26:14.830
ale fabriklekh farmakht,

00:26:14.867 --> 00:26:18.152
azoy me iz gegangen in gas arayn, azoy vi me geyt haynt in Yerusholaim.

00:26:18.613 --> 00:26:21.982
aroys mit di kapotes, bay di frume, mit di taleysim,

00:26:22.190 --> 00:26:24.125
un un gegangen in shuln arayn.

00:26:24.857 --> 00:26:26.269
geven zeyer a

00:26:26.561 --> 00:26:29.056
interesant tsu zen in aza

00:26:29.056 --> 00:26:30.656
antisemitish land

00:26:31.151 --> 00:26:33.061
yidn zoln zikh geyn fray.

00:26:33.277 --> 00:26:40.460
hot geven a untershid tsvishn in Varsh- tsvishn di varshever yidn, tsvishn di raykhe un oreme yidn?

00:26:40.095 --> 00:26:41.687
a groyser untershid.

00:26:41.698 --> 00:26:44.342
se geven a zeyer a kleyne protsent raykhe yidn.

00:26:44.415 --> 00:26:47.683
oder vifl ikh ken nisht genoy zogn dem protsent, se geven

00:26:47.891 --> 00:26:51.786
a iberflus, se geven a geshikhte fun a zibetsik protsent, akhtsik protsent

00:26:51.806 --> 00:26:55.175
iz geven azoy bal-melokhelekh,

00:26:55.485 --> 00:27:00.323
zey hobn koym gezhiplet fun der parnose, se geven zeyer a sakh oreme layt,

00:27:00.463 --> 00:27:02.077
azoy az se

00:27:02.370 --> 00:27:05.706
geven zeyer a sakh. se geven raykhe mentshn vos zey hobn gehat hayzer,

00:27:06.200 --> 00:27:08.051
zenen geven ⟨UNK⟩layt,

00:27:08.394 --> 00:27:12.287
azoy az di ge- zey hobn groyse gesheftn in yidishn gegnt,

00:27:12.444 --> 00:27:16.390
azoy zenen geven bal-parnosedik, nor dos rov iz geven

00:27:16.393 --> 00:27:20.589
di vos hobn gearbet bay yenem un di vos hobn gearbet far zikh in a kleyne ort vu zey hobn,

00:27:20.696 --> 00:27:24.819
zey hobn adurkhgemakht, zey hobn nisht gehat keyn dires, se geven zeyer tayer dire gelt,

00:27:24.864 --> 00:27:27.899
me hot zhe nisht gekent tsoln far keyn dires ven se geven shver,

00:27:27.935 --> 00:27:29.836
az nisht hot men dikh aroysgevorfn,

00:27:30.264 --> 00:27:34.573
azoy az di oreme layt hobn gelebt a sakh mol in kelers, veyst vos a keler iz,

00:27:34.601 --> 00:27:36.910
un a mol in boydem, vu me hengt vesh,

00:27:36.913 --> 00:27:39.726
un dos iz geven zeyer a ofter ershaynung.

00:27:40.912 --> 00:27:43.927
geven an oreme klas iz geven zeyer a groyser

00:27:44.000 --> 00:27:44.990
in Varshe.

00:27:44.979 --> 00:27:46.678
un dayn mishpokhe?

00:27:46.734 --> 00:27:50.086
mayn mishpokhe nor vos me hot zikh basheftikt aleyn,

00:27:50.582 --> 00:27:53.701
me hot nisht badorfn gebn keynem keyn WAGES, azoy

00:27:53.703 --> 00:27:57.444
az tsvishn di kinder hot men basheftikt, me hot gearbet biz der tate

00:27:57.669 --> 00:28:01.410
iz geven shoyn nisht feik tsu der arbet, hobn undz ibergenumen

00:28:01.837 --> 00:28:03.080
dem varshtat.

00:28:04.217 --> 00:28:09.621
un vos hot pasirt tsum tatn nokh di muter's toyt?

00:28:08.351 --> 00:28:09.679
nokh di milkhome?

00:28:09.621 --> 00:28:12.260
neyn, nokh, nokh di muter's toyt.

00:28:10.764 --> 00:28:11.838
f- nokh de-

00:28:12.688 --> 00:28:13.914
nokhn toyt?

00:28:13.312 --> 00:28:14.988
muter's toyt.

00:28:14.988 --> 00:28:16.035
fun di vayb,

00:28:16.035 --> 00:28:18.100
ven dayn muter iz geshtorb-

00:28:16.383 --> 00:28:19.702
ah ven di froy iz geshtorbn, farshteyt zikh er iz geblibn aleyn.

00:28:19.877 --> 00:28:21.612
azoy az er hot shoyn nisht

00:28:21.612 --> 00:28:22.740
mitgearbet,

00:28:23.117 --> 00:28:26.033
un er iz zikh gegangen efsher shpatsirn, iz er geven,

00:28:26.033 --> 00:28:29.405
un in yidishn gegnt iz dort geven zeyer a sheyner park,

00:28:29.799 --> 00:28:34.192
dos iz dos Kashinski's Gortn hot er geheysn, iz geven spetsyel a yidisher gortn,

00:28:34.192 --> 00:28:36.605
dort hobn zikh azoy getrofn zikh yidn

00:28:36.633 --> 00:28:41.420
un gezesn oyf di benk un a bisl gemotlt, geredt politik, ir veyst dokh vi nokh bay yidn iz.

00:28:41.645 --> 00:28:46.871
azoy der foter, az du vilst visn vu er der foter iz gegangen, vu er iz, ken ikh dir zogn,

00:28:47.012 --> 00:28:49.622
der foter iz opgeven a gevise tsayt

00:28:51.821 --> 00:28:53.042
un er iz

00:28:53.053 --> 00:28:55.075
hot z- hot gevolt durkhoys

00:28:55.112 --> 00:28:57.317
shtarbn in Yisroel.

00:28:57.440 --> 00:28:58.987
dos iz geven zayn bager.

00:28:59.735 --> 00:29:02.365
un er hot ongehoybn tsu k- tsu firn,

00:29:02.385 --> 00:29:03.681
heyst tsu kemfn,

00:29:03.681 --> 00:29:08.457
az me zol im, az di englender hobn nisht gevolt araynlozn keyn yidn; ven di englender hobn gehat di mandat,

00:29:08.477 --> 00:29:09.967
in PALESTINE,

00:29:09.995 --> 00:29:12.183
hot men nisht keyn yidn gevolt araynlozn.

00:29:13.185 --> 00:29:16.099
un er hot zikh oysgearbet zikh aza sort

00:29:16.239 --> 00:29:18.562
vize, vi azoy es ruft zikh, a pa-

00:29:18.703 --> 00:29:21.198
az az Bnei Brak

00:29:21.217 --> 00:29:23.037
darf hobn a rov,

00:29:23.057 --> 00:29:26.201
un er fodert aroys fun Poyln a rov, un der foter

00:29:26.201 --> 00:29:27.286
hot dos

00:29:27.613 --> 00:29:29.348
gemakht zikh dem dem

00:29:29.351 --> 00:29:31.390
tsi vize, tsi a pasport,

00:29:31.393 --> 00:29:34.267
un er hot oyfgeshribn a- az er iz a rov,

00:29:34.295 --> 00:29:36.821
er iz nisht geven keyn rov, o er iz geven a a

00:29:36.894 --> 00:29:39.844
religyeze mentsh, ober keyn rov iz er nisht geven,

00:29:39.844 --> 00:29:44.999
un mit i- azoy iz er araynbakumen zikh keyn Bnei Brak; Bnei Brak iz zeyer a frumer shtot,

00:29:44.999 --> 00:29:45.970
nokh bay,

00:29:45.014 --> 00:29:46.082
aleyns?

00:29:45.990 --> 00:29:48.853
aley- neyn, er iz geforn mit a froy, a tsveyte froy.

00:29:49.128 --> 00:29:52.818
dos iz geven a vayte vayte mishpokhe,

00:29:52.942 --> 00:29:56.179
a kuz- a vayte kuzinke fun dritn dor,

00:29:56.199 --> 00:29:57.560
azoy er hot ir,

00:29:58.157 --> 00:30:00.412
azoy er hot ir farheyrat,

00:30:00.485 --> 00:30:02.774
un er iz avek nokh PALESTINE. ALL RIGHT?

00:30:03.590 --> 00:30:05.863
un er iz geshtorbn in,

00:30:05.835 --> 00:30:07.449
er iz geshtorbn in PALESTINE.

00:30:07.607 --> 00:30:09.154
gedenkst dem yor?

00:30:09.345 --> 00:30:11.364
yo, dos yor ikh gleyb

00:30:12.129 --> 00:30:15.650
er iz avek in draysikstn. in akht un draysikstn yor.

00:30:15.909 --> 00:30:19.346
iz er dort nifter gevorn, zey hobn ge- a rov vert nifter,

00:30:19.419 --> 00:30:20.983
e zogt nisht geshtorbn.

00:30:23.537 --> 00:30:24.342
a da-
